These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, 7up, tea
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the photographer is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the designer##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the photographer is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | fishing  | camping | card-games |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Beverage   | tea       | 7up      | soy-milk | sprite      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

