.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, canadian, egyptian, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the french is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the french is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the egyptian##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | canadian       | french     | dutch    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

