.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, climbing, snowboarding
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical, scientific
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, mouse, pony
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the pony##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Sport      | cricket | basketball       | snowboarding        | climbing        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror    | scientific | musical        |
| Pet           | mouse         | hedgehog  | pony       | lizard         |

