.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, sudoku, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hedgehog, pony
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, emerald, fuchsia, green
 1. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who likes green is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | coffee | fanta     | iced-tea    | mirinda |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| Pet         | frog   | hedgehog  | pony        | bird    |
| Color   | green   | emerald | blue    | fuchsia |

