.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, milk, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, october, july
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel, western, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, scooter, skateboard
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person drinking water is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | water      | 7up         | milk        | juice      |
| Birthday           | december | february | october  | july  |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | musical     | time-travel | zombie     |
| Transport     | bus        | scooter     | jet-ski     | skateboard |

