.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, drawing, video-games, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, classical, disco, metal
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, mouse, pony
House: cottage, art-deco, cape-cod, victorian
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the victorian house is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the cape-cod house is the owner of the frog##1
8. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
9. the fan of metal is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | video-games | baking     |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | metal       | blues       | classical  |
| Pet           | pony    | hedgehog    | mouse       | frog       |
| House     | cottage     | victorian        | art-deco   | cape-cod |

