The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, traveling, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, light-blue, ivory, yellow
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, sailing, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking tea##1
9. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | tea           | juice    | lemonade    |
| Hobby         | traveling  | rock-climbing | drawing  | video-games |
| Color   | ivory     | lilac     | light-blue | yellow   |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton     | biathlon | sailing     |

